title: Sports Insight - March/April 2016
description:
English | 67 pages | PDF | 20.4 MB

Trade magazine for all independent sports retailers throughout the UK. Of interest also to sporting goods/apparel/footwear/equipment wholesalers and manufacturers. The leading title to serve this extensive market. Up-to-the-minute industry news, vacancies, new products, contacts and advice - it's an essential read for anyone associated with the retail market
